ially refer to such a\nstrategy implementation for the LSST as the Presto-Color strategy\n(rapid-color). This cadence's minimal requirements allow for overall\noptimization of a survey for other science goals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Dec 2018 18:13:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Apr 2019 03:38:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-30"}
