ue\nthat correctly predicts routes selected by the current navigation system of the\nLondon Ambulance Service and our best performing speed estimation model. This\nhybrid approach outperforms alternative mobility models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Dec 2018 19:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-11"}
