harge. We provide prospective bounds for $\\sqrt{s} =\n13$ TeV LHC searches at integrated luminosities of 39.5 fb${}^{-1}$, 100\nfb${}^{-1}$, and 300 fb${}^{-1}$. Moreover, we show that a joint observation in\nthe open and the closed channels allows to determine the mass, spin, color, and\nelectric charge of the particle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Dec 2018 19:00:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Apr 2019 16:32:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
