asible and accurate. This\nmethod is helpful for analyzing and extracting useful information from a large\nnumber of experimental values and then providing a reference for discovering\nphysical laws and support for physical experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Dec 2018 02:01:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2018 09:06:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 00:03:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-18"}
